官方数据，今年中国重新成为德国第一大贸易伙伴，超过了因贸易战而受影响的美国。","newsLink":"https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85/20251119-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BA%E5%BE%B7%E5%9B%BD%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%A4%A7%E8%B4%B8%E6%98%93%E4%BC%99%E4%BC%B4-%E5%AF%B9%E5%8D%8E%E8%B4%B8%E6%98%93%E9%80%86%E5%B7%AE%E8%BE%BE647%E4%BA%BF%E6%AC%A7%E5%85%83","thumbnail":"","detailImage":"news/detail/rfi/2025/11/19/1763572419000.webp","sourceId":"rfi"}]